mixin headline(tClass, desktopFontInfo, mobileFontInfo)
  +demo
    h4.uncap.cls .#{tClass}
    p(class=tClass) Donec rhoncus turpis mi, id elementum.
    p.info.visible-desktop= desktopFontInfo
    p.info.visible-phone= mobileFontInfo

mixin bodyCopy(pClass, desktopFontInfo, mobileFontInfo)
  +demo
    h4.uncap.cls .#{pClass}
    p(class=pClass) Donec rhoncus turpis mi, id elementum nunc dapibus eu. Suspendisse varius tempor elit vitae vehicula. Praesent volutpat ultrices quam. Vivamus cursus enim dolor, non venenatis ligula sollicitudin in. Donec rhoncus turpis mi, id elementum nunc dapibus eu. Suspendisse varius tempor elit vitae vehicula. Praesent volutpat ultrices quam. Vivamus cursus enim dolor, non venenatis ligula sollicitudin in.
    p.info.visible-desktop= desktopFontInfo
    p.info.visible-phone= mobileFontInfo

mixin swatch(color, title, hex)
  .span2
    .swatch(class="bg-" + color)
    .p1= title
    h5= hex

